Scope note (not part of the MIT grant above):

- The MIT license applies to the SOURCE CODE in this repository.
- The bulk training data and the large trained model weights (e.g. v3-37M and
  the other models under model/) are NOT covered by this license and are not
  distributed here (they are gitignored). They derive in part from TWIC
  (theweekinchess.com), whose terms are "personal use only", so that data and
  the weights derived from it are personal-use only and must not be
  redistributed wholesale.
- One small set of weights IS published: the browser Model Capsule under
  viz/public/weights/ (the ~116k-parameter distilled net the web tool runs).
  It is committed and deployed to GitHub Pages solely so the web app works, and
  is provided for use within this web tool only. Because it too derives in part
  from TWIC (personal-use) data, NO separate redistribution or reuse grant is
  made for these weights — the MIT grant above does not extend to them.
- Third-party assets bundled with the web tool retain their own licenses; see
  viz/THIRD_PARTY.md for attribution.

See the README "Provenance and license" section.
